1
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:56,950
Your Highness,

2
00:01:57,350 --> 00:01:58,400
last night,

3
00:01:58,870 --> 00:02:00,310
you and Liu Chu...

4
00:02:06,230 --> 00:02:07,680
From this moment on,

5
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:10,190
you are his true concubine.

6
00:02:11,630 --> 00:02:13,280
Rank doesn't matter.

7
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:14,840
What matters

8
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:16,630
is that he keeps loving me.

9
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,680
I’m sure he will.

10
00:02:21,870 --> 00:02:22,680
By the way, Your Highness,

11
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:23,150
Yes?

12
00:02:23,870 --> 00:02:26,430
I'm leaving the palace today.

13
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:30,960
So soon?

14
00:02:31,680 --> 00:02:32,470
Yes.

15
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:35,630
Lan said she has found
a place for me to stay.【】

16
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:38,820
She hopes I can leave as soon as possible.

17
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:40,840
Well...

18
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,030
Don't worry.

19
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:45,300
Now that you and Liu Chu
have shared your wedding night,

20
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:46,760
I can finally be at ease.

21
00:02:48,470 --> 00:02:50,030
What if I miss you?

22
00:02:50,870 --> 00:02:51,870
I told you.

23
00:02:52,150 --> 00:02:54,480
I’ll come back to visit you
as soon as I can.

24
00:02:55,870 --> 00:02:56,960
Really?

25
00:02:57,840 --> 00:02:58,470
Yes.

26
00:03:04,630 --> 00:03:05,960
Such a beauty—

27
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,690
who could help but fall in love?

28
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,860
Then in the future,

29
00:03:12,190 --> 00:03:14,190
I’ll have to find you the perfect husband,

30
00:03:14,190 --> 00:03:16,079
and marry you off in grand style.

31
00:03:19,630 --> 00:03:21,150
I still prefer

32
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,870
Changmo men.

33
00:03:26,079 --> 00:03:26,470
Then...

34
00:03:26,470 --> 00:03:28,280
Lord Fei has no chance, right?

35
00:03:36,190 --> 00:03:37,280
Because Miss Jin Xi

36
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:39,000
is Consort Ling's female official.

37
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:41,030
the Grand Princess specially ordered
the palace gates opened wide

38
00:03:41,030 --> 00:03:42,079
and personally saw her off

39
00:03:42,079 --> 00:03:43,610
with the highest courtesy.

40
00:03:43,750 --> 00:03:45,870
Not everyone gets this kind of treatment.

41
00:03:45,870 --> 00:03:47,560
Then please, Miss Lan,

42
00:03:47,560 --> 00:03:49,280
convey my thanks
to the Grand Princess for me.

43
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,470
I certainly will.

44
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:53,150
When I'm not around,

45
00:03:53,470 --> 00:03:55,840
if anyone dares to bully the Princess,

46
00:03:56,000 --> 00:03:58,460
I definitely won't
let them get away with it.

47
00:03:58,470 --> 00:04:01,080
Consort Ling is the person
the Emperor cares about the most.

48
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:01,960
In this palace,

49
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:03,870
who would dare to bully her?

50
00:04:04,630 --> 00:04:05,190
Okay.

51
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:07,150
Then I am relieved.

52
00:04:09,870 --> 00:04:11,000
Jin Xi,

53
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:13,610
take good care of yourself.

54
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:15,870
Take care.

55
00:04:20,630 --> 00:04:22,240
Bring Miss Jin Xi’s luggage.

56
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:28,950
Jin Xi,

57
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,450
you must come back to see me.

58
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:55,610
Where are you going?

59
00:04:55,800 --> 00:04:56,870
I'm going to see Mo.

60
00:04:57,159 --> 00:04:57,890
Don't worry.

61
00:04:58,190 --> 00:05:00,070
Liu Xiyang will take good care of him.

62
00:05:00,070 --> 00:05:01,310
Do you need something from me?

63
00:05:01,310 --> 00:05:01,910
Follow me.

64
00:05:30,190 --> 00:05:31,950
Where is this place?

65
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:35,190
This is a warehouse.

66
00:05:35,390 --> 00:05:36,600
It holds some goods.

67
00:05:36,750 --> 00:05:38,750
I want you to help me do an inventory.

68
00:05:40,270 --> 00:05:42,600
I have a feeling
you’re trying to trick me.

69
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:44,060
How could I ever trick you?

70
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:44,770
Let's go.

71
00:05:55,120 --> 00:05:56,630
This isn't a warehouse.

72
00:05:56,630 --> 00:05:58,070
It's clearly a pharmacy.

73
00:05:58,950 --> 00:05:59,870
Take a look at these herbs

74
00:05:59,870 --> 00:06:01,070
and see if they are still usable,

75
00:06:01,070 --> 00:06:02,120
or

76
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:04,000
if you need anything else.

77
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:09,480
Jewel orchid!

78
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,950
This is the king of herbs!

79
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:16,860
And reishi mushrooms!

80
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:19,870
And so much ginseng!

81
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,610
Are these all yours?

82
00:06:24,190 --> 00:06:25,000
Yeah.

83
00:06:25,750 --> 00:06:27,480
This is top-quality medicine.

84
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,740
You've struck it rich?

85
00:06:28,870 --> 00:06:29,680
I...

86
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:31,680
If I gave it to you,

87
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:32,680
what would you do?

88
00:06:33,830 --> 00:06:35,750
If you gave it to me,

89
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:38,040
I could definitely treat more people.

90
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,040
In that case,

91
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:41,300
I'll give you both the herbs and the shop.

92
00:06:41,560 --> 00:06:42,630
Are you really giving them to me?

93
00:06:42,630 --> 00:06:43,230
Of course.

94
00:06:45,190 --> 00:06:47,560
Do you have an ulterior motive?

95
00:06:49,390 --> 00:06:51,830
What ulterior motive
could I have with you?

96
00:06:53,240 --> 00:06:54,630
You’ve been treating me

97
00:06:54,630 --> 00:06:55,800
all this time,

98
00:06:55,870 --> 00:06:57,159
so after I returned to the capital,

99
00:06:57,159 --> 00:06:58,800
I wanted to give you something in return.

100
00:06:58,800 --> 00:06:59,680
But I felt

101
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:01,800
that gold and silver jewelry
are too tacky.

102
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:03,070
Then I thought

103
00:07:03,270 --> 00:07:05,070
you'd probably like a pharmacy.

104
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:06,830
How can I accept

105
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,630
such an expensive gift?

106
00:07:09,390 --> 00:07:10,480
Once I give it to you,

107
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:12,800
won't you be able to treat more people?

108
00:07:13,240 --> 00:07:14,360
Then I'll really accept it?

109
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:14,960
Accept it.

110
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,490
I'll accept it then.

111
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,750
From now on, I'll be here

112
00:07:17,750 --> 00:07:18,950
treating the people.

113
00:07:19,630 --> 00:07:20,950
Then later,

114
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,630
I'll write an inscription for you.

115
00:07:22,630 --> 00:07:23,600
Save the world

116
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:24,800
and bless the people.

117
00:07:24,830 --> 00:07:26,040
I never thought General Xiao

118
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,680
could be so sweet-talking.

119
00:07:38,750 --> 00:07:40,550
You have something on your mind.

120
00:07:42,950 --> 00:07:45,159
I just feel the incident
at Huangpi Village

121
00:07:45,159 --> 00:07:46,220
is not that simple.

122
00:07:47,390 --> 00:07:50,600
The symptoms this time are the same
as the great plague back then.

123
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,830
It reminds me

124
00:07:52,159 --> 00:07:53,360
that our Han family

125
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:55,000
might have offended someone
during that plague

126
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,040
and

127
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:57,190
got persecuted.

128
00:08:00,040 --> 00:08:00,680
Wait.

129
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,240
Have you thought of something?

130
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,600
We need to investigate

131
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,750
among those who survived

132
00:08:04,750 --> 00:08:05,680
that plague.

133
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:07,010
Do you have any targets?

134
00:08:08,070 --> 00:08:10,270
The senior officials
who survived the plague

135
00:08:10,270 --> 00:08:12,160
include Zhang Ruizhong, Lord Zhang,

136
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:14,040
and Wang Ruhai, Lord Wang.

137
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:18,040
Are you saying

138
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:21,040
they are all related to
the massacre of the Han family?

139
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:21,630
Yes.

140
00:08:22,070 --> 00:08:23,330
It's highly possible.

141
00:08:23,630 --> 00:08:24,240
But the details

142
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:26,440
can only be known after investigation.

143
00:08:26,870 --> 00:08:28,480
This Wang Ruhai

144
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,800
is idle at home.

145
00:08:30,270 --> 00:08:31,070
It just so happens

146
00:08:31,070 --> 00:08:32,549
we can try starting with him.

147
00:08:32,549 --> 00:08:33,030
Okay.

148
00:08:35,750 --> 00:08:36,909
Injustice!

149
00:08:36,909 --> 00:08:38,630
The Prince's family is going too far!【】

150
00:08:38,630 --> 00:08:39,789
Let me in!

151
00:08:39,789 --> 00:08:40,360
Who

152
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:41,669
dares to trespass into
the Prince's mansion?

153
00:08:41,669 --> 00:08:44,000
You lawless thugs

154
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:46,670
kidnapped my daughter in broad daylight!

155
00:08:46,670 --> 00:08:47,120
I...

156
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:48,670
I will sue you at the government office

157
00:08:48,670 --> 00:08:50,630
and let you get the punishment
you deserve!

158
00:08:50,630 --> 00:08:51,440
Sue me?

159
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:54,080
Do you think the government office
will accept

160
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:55,840
the lawsuit of a commoner like you?

161
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,030
How ridiculous.

162
00:08:57,030 --> 00:08:58,390
Justice will prevail!

163
00:08:58,390 --> 00:08:59,720
I will let everyone in the world

164
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:01,240
know of your evil deeds!

165
00:09:01,550 --> 00:09:02,630
Give me back my daughter!

166
00:09:02,630 --> 00:09:04,360
Give me back my daughter!

167
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:04,910
You...

168
00:09:05,630 --> 00:09:06,510
Fine.

169
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,080
I'll let you sue me.

170
00:09:08,240 --> 00:09:10,240
Let everyone see

171
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:11,770
what a crazy old man you are.

172
00:09:14,030 --> 00:09:17,240
Give me back my daughter!

173
00:09:20,080 --> 00:09:20,870
My lord.

174
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:31,080
This old fool

175
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,750
has a death wish.

176
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:35,670
How dare he sue me.

177
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:36,670
Yes, my lord.

178
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,810
If no one was instigating this,

179
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:39,960
who in the capital

180
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,630
would dare to cross you?

181
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,390
Makes sense.

182
00:09:46,270 --> 00:09:48,670
I've been recovering at home these days.

183
00:09:48,670 --> 00:09:50,400
I haven't done anything wrong.

184
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,060
Who could I have offended?

185
00:09:52,150 --> 00:09:54,270
Could it be that brat Xiao Chi?

186
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:55,630
After all, our young master

187
00:09:55,630 --> 00:09:57,360
had a feud with him before.

188
00:09:58,200 --> 00:09:59,550
Xiao Chi?

189
00:10:01,390 --> 00:10:02,750
Xiao Chi!

190
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:04,240
It was because of him

191
00:10:04,240 --> 00:10:06,480
that His Majesty made me
stay idle at home.

192
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:07,000
He...

193
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:08,860
Now he wants to mess with me again.

194
00:10:09,550 --> 00:10:10,550
He thinks

195
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:11,750
that just by doing this,

196
00:10:11,750 --> 00:10:13,550
he can threaten the Wang family?

197
00:10:15,670 --> 00:10:17,670
Xiao Chi!

198
00:10:17,670 --> 00:10:19,330
Take that for threatening me!

199
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:20,840
My lord!

200
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:23,000
I spent a fortune

201
00:10:23,030 --> 00:10:24,480
to borrow this
from the Ministry of Justice.

202
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,480
I still have to return it.

203
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,670
Xiao Chi!

204
00:10:26,670 --> 00:10:27,870
I am not done with him.

205
00:10:53,030 --> 00:10:55,000
Why would I have such a nightmare?

206
00:11:38,670 --> 00:11:39,670
What's wrong?

207
00:11:41,480 --> 00:11:42,840
I had a nightmare.

208
00:11:43,270 --> 00:11:44,000
A nightmare?

209
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:46,760
What did you dream about?

210
00:11:48,150 --> 00:11:51,030
I dreamed that Huangbei Village
was engulfed in flames.

211
00:11:51,030 --> 00:11:53,090
The villagers were all slaughtered.

212
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:59,150
Come with me.

213
00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:56,670
Run!

214
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,630
Hurry!

215
00:13:02,150 --> 00:13:03,410
How could this happen?

216
00:13:04,030 --> 00:13:06,490
What did these villagers
do to deserve this?

217
00:13:07,630 --> 00:13:09,480
We must make them pay.

218
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:48,670
The hidden weapons are poisoned.

219
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:49,390
Xiao Chi,

220
00:13:49,390 --> 00:13:50,360
hang in there.

221
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:51,150
Bear with it a little longer.

222
00:13:51,150 --> 00:13:51,960
I'm fine.

223
00:13:52,790 --> 00:13:53,990
I'm glad you're okay.

224
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:55,030
I'm fine.

225
00:13:55,030 --> 00:13:56,840
Bear with it, Xiao Chi.

226
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:15,240
I'm sorry.

227
00:14:16,240 --> 00:14:17,080
Bear with it.

228
00:14:17,080 --> 00:14:18,280
Just a little longer.

229
00:14:22,870 --> 00:14:24,150
Hang in there.

230
00:14:25,150 --> 00:14:27,280
I'll go prepare some medicine for you.

231
00:14:40,600 --> 00:14:41,480
Boss.

232
00:14:43,750 --> 00:14:44,680
We don't have it.

233
00:15:08,390 --> 00:15:08,910
No.

234
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:11,480
No.

235
00:15:33,030 --> 00:15:34,240
Lord Fei.

236
00:15:35,360 --> 00:15:36,290
Physician Wang,

237
00:15:37,630 --> 00:15:38,750
what kind of poison is on the dart?

238
00:15:38,750 --> 00:15:39,810
Have you found out?

239
00:15:39,870 --> 00:15:42,440
The dart is coated with
the venom of a krait.

240
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:44,200
Krait venom?

241
00:15:45,550 --> 00:15:46,600
Is there a cure?

242
00:15:46,790 --> 00:15:47,910
Blue snake tail

243
00:15:47,910 --> 00:15:49,750
and snake herb can cure it.

244
00:15:50,000 --> 00:15:51,750
But these are just legends,

245
00:15:51,960 --> 00:15:53,220
and cannot be trusted.

246
00:15:53,270 --> 00:15:54,200
Physician Wang,

247
00:15:54,550 --> 00:15:55,670
you have been a physician for many years,

248
00:15:55,670 --> 00:15:57,360
and are the best physician
in Jinglan.

249
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:59,390
I believe you must have other ways.

250
00:16:00,200 --> 00:16:01,860
As long as Xiao Chi can wake up,

251
00:16:02,080 --> 00:16:03,360
no matter what herbs,

252
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:06,200
I, Fei Zheng, will not hesitate
even if I go bankrupt.

253
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:07,600
To detoxify this,

254
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:09,080
using medicine won't work.

255
00:16:09,080 --> 00:16:11,240
Try using poison against poison.

256
00:16:11,360 --> 00:16:13,240
It might be effective.

257
00:16:13,550 --> 00:16:14,880
Poison against poison?

258
00:16:15,390 --> 00:16:17,390
Physician Wang, please elaborate.

259
00:16:18,030 --> 00:16:20,000
We are good at using medicine,

260
00:16:20,030 --> 00:16:21,480
but when it comes to poison,

261
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:23,030
none of us are good at it.

262
00:16:23,270 --> 00:16:25,200
Fortunately, Physician Han

263
00:16:25,200 --> 00:16:27,390
protected General Xiao's heart meridian.

264
00:16:27,390 --> 00:16:29,150
Even if he doesn't wake up,

265
00:16:29,150 --> 00:16:31,030
his condition won't worsen.

266
00:16:31,480 --> 00:16:32,390
So,

267
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:34,630
our hope can really only rest on

268
00:16:34,630 --> 00:16:35,870
Physician Han.

269
00:16:36,670 --> 00:16:37,530
Physician Han.

270
00:16:37,550 --> 00:16:40,550
The herb you need is not available
in the entire capital.

271
00:16:40,550 --> 00:16:41,210
The Emperor

272
00:16:41,390 --> 00:16:42,630
has also ordered
the Imperial Medical Academy's

273
00:16:42,630 --> 00:16:44,760
physicians to do their best to find it.

274
00:16:45,030 --> 00:16:46,430
I wonder if Physician Han

275
00:16:46,550 --> 00:16:48,000
has any other solutions.

276
00:16:49,270 --> 00:16:50,840
Before we find the medicine,

277
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:52,480
I'll try using other medicines

278
00:16:52,480 --> 00:16:54,810
to stabilize Xiao Chi's condition first.

279
00:17:18,069 --> 00:17:19,069
I found out.

280
00:17:19,640 --> 00:17:20,569
It's Wang Ruhai.

281
00:17:21,270 --> 00:17:22,680
Wang Ruhai?

282
00:17:24,030 --> 00:17:26,030
Why did he want to kill Xiao Chi?

283
00:17:27,270 --> 00:17:29,680
Since the general returned to the capital,

284
00:17:30,030 --> 00:17:31,550
he impeached Wang Ruhai,

285
00:17:32,070 --> 00:17:33,480
causing him to be dismissed

286
00:17:33,480 --> 00:17:35,160
and ostracized by his colleagues,

287
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:35,880
so

288
00:17:36,160 --> 00:17:37,820
he wanted to kill the general.

289
00:17:38,830 --> 00:17:39,680
Lord Zhang

290
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:41,590
is also targeting the general.

291
00:17:41,590 --> 00:17:43,440
Are they targeting Xiao Chi,

292
00:17:43,960 --> 00:17:45,480
or our Han family?

293
00:17:49,960 --> 00:17:51,440
This is the evidence

294
00:17:51,880 --> 00:17:52,400
that Xiao Chi gathered

295
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:54,930
of Wang Ruhai's crimes
before he was injured.

296
00:17:55,830 --> 00:17:56,750
So much?

297
00:17:57,960 --> 00:18:00,750
Are these all the evil deeds
done by Wang Ruhai alone?

298
00:18:00,750 --> 00:18:02,080
This is only a part of it.

299
00:18:02,400 --> 00:18:03,750
There are even more

300
00:18:03,750 --> 00:18:06,160
petitions accusing
him and his son of bullying,

301
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:07,240
running amok,

302
00:18:07,240 --> 00:18:08,640
and coercing trades

303
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:10,560
stored in the boxes outside.

304
00:18:11,030 --> 00:18:12,440
I really can't figure out

305
00:18:13,000 --> 00:18:14,400
why the late Emperor kept

306
00:18:14,480 --> 00:18:16,480
someone like Wang Ruhai by his side.

307
00:18:16,590 --> 00:18:17,960
The late emperor suddenly

308
00:18:17,960 --> 00:18:19,480
fell seriously ill and passed away.

309
00:18:19,480 --> 00:18:20,880
There must be many things

310
00:18:21,030 --> 00:18:22,200
that were not thoroughly considered.

311
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:22,960
However,

312
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:25,800
although Wang Ruhai
has done all kinds of evil,

313
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:27,960
he indeed has prestige in the court.

314
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:29,240
For a man like him,

315
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:31,880
who is greedy and entirely selfish,

316
00:18:32,640 --> 00:18:34,500
if anyone touches his interests,

317
00:18:34,880 --> 00:18:35,940
he will inevitably

318
00:18:36,310 --> 00:18:38,040
fight to the death to stop them.

319
00:18:38,640 --> 00:18:39,400
Then tell me,

320
00:18:39,720 --> 00:18:40,750
what should I do?

321
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:43,620
Evil people

322
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:45,370
should be punished.

323
00:18:45,480 --> 00:18:47,440
Since he dares to
secretly harm the Third Brother now,

324
00:18:47,440 --> 00:18:48,240
who knows

325
00:18:48,240 --> 00:18:50,970
what outrageous things
he might do in the future.

326
00:18:53,110 --> 00:18:53,960
The court

327
00:18:53,960 --> 00:18:56,400
will decide my fate.

328
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:59,030
It is not your place to question me.

329
00:19:02,790 --> 00:19:03,960
Go back.

330
00:19:08,400 --> 00:19:09,590
Can you tell me

331
00:19:09,590 --> 00:19:12,520
the truth about
the extermination of the Han family?

332
00:19:15,270 --> 00:19:17,960
As for the truth
about the extermination of the Han family,

333
00:19:17,960 --> 00:19:19,350
even if I knew,

334
00:19:20,070 --> 00:19:22,110
I wouldn't tell you.

335
00:19:22,680 --> 00:19:23,200
You!

336
00:19:24,830 --> 00:19:26,000
By imperial order:

337
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:27,640
all unrelated personnel

338
00:19:27,640 --> 00:19:28,570
are to withdraw.

339
00:19:31,440 --> 00:19:33,680
Investigation reveals
Wang Kun, son of Wang Ruhai,

340
00:19:33,680 --> 00:19:35,280
kidnapped a commoner woman.

341
00:19:35,550 --> 00:19:37,680
Wang Ruhai failed to discipline his son.

342
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:39,160
His past crimes

343
00:19:39,240 --> 00:19:40,640
are too numerous to count.

344
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:41,640
It is hereby ordered

345
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:42,830
that he be dismissed and investigated,

346
00:19:42,830 --> 00:19:45,560
and his son Wang Kun
be imprisoned pending trial.

347
00:19:45,960 --> 00:19:47,090
This is impossible.

348
00:19:47,240 --> 00:19:48,370
This is impossible.

349
00:19:49,270 --> 00:19:49,960
Father,

350
00:19:49,960 --> 00:19:50,880
I'm innocent!

351
00:19:50,880 --> 00:19:51,480
Father,

352
00:19:51,480 --> 00:19:52,480
they framed me!

353
00:19:52,480 --> 00:19:52,960
Father!

354
00:19:52,960 --> 00:19:53,400
I know.

355
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:53,860
Father.

356
00:19:54,240 --> 00:19:54,830
Save me, Father!

357
00:19:54,830 --> 00:19:55,240
Take him down.

358
00:19:55,240 --> 00:19:55,720
Don't panic.

359
00:19:55,720 --> 00:19:56,650
Father, save me!

360
00:19:57,310 --> 00:19:58,070
Father!

361
00:19:58,400 --> 00:19:58,880
Father!

362
00:19:59,160 --> 00:20:00,030
Save me, Father!

363
00:20:00,030 --> 00:20:00,880
Impossible. They framed me!

364
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:01,830
Stop!

365
00:20:01,830 --> 00:20:02,680
Let go!

366
00:20:03,440 --> 00:20:05,700
Who dares to cause trouble in my mansion?

367
00:20:06,200 --> 00:20:08,030
We cannot disobey the imperial order.

368
00:20:08,030 --> 00:20:08,880
Take him away.

369
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:09,440
Son!

370
00:20:09,440 --> 00:20:10,030
Father!

371
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:10,920
Son!

372
00:20:11,550 --> 00:20:12,270
Father!

373
00:20:13,750 --> 00:20:14,400
Son!

374
00:20:14,400 --> 00:20:15,350
Save me, Father!

375
00:20:18,030 --> 00:20:18,720
I know.

376
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:20,070
I know you are investigating

377
00:20:20,070 --> 00:20:21,330
the Han family matter.

378
00:20:21,350 --> 00:20:22,110
I

379
00:20:22,440 --> 00:20:23,830
will tell you the truth.

380
00:20:23,830 --> 00:20:25,030
Let my son go,

381
00:20:25,030 --> 00:20:26,400
and I'll tell you the truth.

382
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:27,640
What is the truth?

383
00:20:27,640 --> 00:20:28,500
The truth is...

384
00:20:32,350 --> 00:20:33,480
Tell me now!

385
00:20:33,480 --> 00:20:34,550
Tell me now!

386
00:20:34,550 --> 00:20:37,070
What is the truth
behind the massacre of the Han family?

387
00:20:37,070 --> 00:20:37,960
The truth is...

388
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:40,350
Wang Ruhai, tell me now!

389
00:20:40,350 --> 00:20:42,110
What is the truth?

390
00:21:03,640 --> 00:21:05,750
Eldest Princess, Wang Ruhai is dead.

391
00:21:07,270 --> 00:21:08,270
How did he die?

392
00:21:09,030 --> 00:21:10,960
When the Emperor
ordered the capture of his son,

393
00:21:10,960 --> 00:21:12,000
he fainted,

394
00:21:12,200 --> 00:21:13,880
and never woke up again.

395
00:21:14,350 --> 00:21:17,200
His crimes were enough
to have him paraded through the streets.

396
00:21:17,200 --> 00:21:18,070
Dying like this

397
00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:19,770
is letting him off easy.

398
00:21:20,550 --> 00:21:22,200
The regent left by the late Emperor

399
00:21:22,200 --> 00:21:23,460
is just gone like that.

400
00:21:25,240 --> 00:21:26,770
This is just the beginning.

401
00:21:27,640 --> 00:21:29,400
Lord Zhang is getting old.

402
00:21:29,680 --> 00:21:31,590
He probably won't last for
many more years.

403
00:21:31,590 --> 00:21:32,510
Then,

404
00:21:32,720 --> 00:21:35,270
should we secretly befriend Li Shichang?

405
00:21:35,480 --> 00:21:38,640
A Princess having close ties
with a minister

406
00:21:39,030 --> 00:21:40,760
will definitely cause gossip.

407
00:21:43,880 --> 00:21:45,030
Not just him.

408
00:21:45,790 --> 00:21:47,650
Xiao Chi has been sick for so long,

409
00:21:47,960 --> 00:21:50,090
and we didn't visit him either, did we?

410
00:21:51,070 --> 00:21:53,030
As long as the Emperor is obedient,

411
00:21:53,480 --> 00:21:54,640
all of Jinglan

412
00:21:55,160 --> 00:21:57,030
will be under my control.

413
00:21:59,550 --> 00:22:00,350
By the way,

414
00:22:01,550 --> 00:22:02,960
how is that female official?

415
00:22:02,960 --> 00:22:03,960
We've already arranged for her

416
00:22:03,960 --> 00:22:05,690
to stay in our outer residence.

417
00:22:05,750 --> 00:22:08,270
Everyone there belongs to
our Xie Shadow Guard.【】

418
00:22:08,270 --> 00:22:10,030
The tribute ambassador
from Changmo is coming soon.

419
00:22:10,030 --> 00:22:11,490
Keep a close eye on things.

420
00:22:11,640 --> 00:22:12,310
Understood.

421
00:22:12,310 --> 00:22:13,570
I'll take my leave now.

422
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:38,300
Even though you haven't woken up yet,

423
00:22:38,590 --> 00:22:40,070
I believe you can

424
00:22:40,070 --> 00:22:41,550
hear what I'm saying.

425
00:22:43,200 --> 00:22:45,640
I'm going to the North Mountain
to pick an herb.

426
00:22:45,640 --> 00:22:46,680
With it,

427
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:48,960
you will definitely wake up.

428
00:22:54,200 --> 00:22:56,030
You must hold on.

429
00:22:57,720 --> 00:22:58,920
Wait for me to return.

430
00:23:04,550 --> 00:23:07,000
This journey has been full of hardships,

431
00:23:07,480 --> 00:23:10,080
and you have always been
the one protecting me.

432
00:23:10,640 --> 00:23:11,790
Now it's my turn

433
00:23:12,790 --> 00:23:14,200
to protect you.

434
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:22,830
Xiao Chi,

435
00:23:23,640 --> 00:23:24,440
wait for me.

436
00:23:37,960 --> 00:23:38,640
Lord Fei.

437
00:23:38,830 --> 00:23:39,550
Chengfeng,

438
00:23:42,830 --> 00:23:44,550
you've been guarding for quite a while.

439
00:23:44,550 --> 00:23:45,680
Go back and rest.

440
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:46,940
I can take it from here.

441
00:23:47,680 --> 00:23:49,240
I wouldn't be able to sleep anyway.

442
00:23:49,240 --> 00:23:50,200
Being here

443
00:23:50,350 --> 00:23:52,270
actually makes me feel more at ease.

444
00:23:52,270 --> 00:23:53,070
Alright.

445
00:23:54,030 --> 00:23:54,640
Take a seat.

446
00:23:54,640 --> 00:23:56,300
I'll stay with you for a while.

447
00:23:56,350 --> 00:23:56,830
Sit.

448
00:26:53,880 --> 00:26:54,740
Physician Han.

449
00:26:56,270 --> 00:26:56,960
Physician Han,

450
00:26:56,960 --> 00:26:57,750
you're back.

451
00:27:02,160 --> 00:27:03,020
Physician Han!

452
00:27:03,830 --> 00:27:04,640
Physician Han!
